'''Akarere ka Balâ''' (izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Balâ ilçesi'' ) ni akarere kari mu [[Intara y’Ankara|ntara y’Ankara]] y’igihugu cya [[Turukiya]]. Akarere ka Balâ ni kamwe mu turere 16 tugize Intara y’Ankara. Akarere gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 29.239 (abagabo 14.749 n’abagore 14.490)<ref>[http://report.tuik.gov.tr/reports/rwservlet?adnksdb2=&report=idari_yapi_2008.RDF&p_il1=6&p_yil=2008&desformat=html&ENVID=adnksdb2Env  TÜİK]</ref> , batuye kubuso bwa km² 2.830 .

== Akarere gahana imbibe ==
Gahana imbibi na:
:Mu majyaruguru :  Akarere ka [[Çankaya]], Akarere ka [[Mamak]] n’Akarere k’[[Elmadağ]]
:Mu burasirazuba : [[Intara ya Kırıkkale]] n’[[Intara ya Kırşehir]]
:Mu majyepfo : Akarere ka [[Şereflikoçhisar]] n’[[Intara ya Konya]]
:Mu burengerazuba : Akarere ka [[Haymana]] n’Akarere ka [[Gölbaşı]]

